tps://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Skepta-and-Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-Big-Smoke-Corporation-and-MEGA_GC-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Skepta 和 Kanye West。图片来源：Dave Benett/Getty Images for Big Smoke Corporation 和 MEGA/GC Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Skepta-and-Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-Big-Smoke-Corporation-and-MEGA_GC-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Skepta-and-Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-Big-Smoke-Corporation-and-MEGA_GC-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Skepta-and-Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-Big-Smoke-Corporation-and-MEGA_GC-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Skepta-and-Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-Big-Smoke-Corporation-and-MEGA_GC-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Skepta-and-Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-Big-Smoke-Corporation-and-MEGA_GC-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Skepta-and-Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-Big-Smoke-Corporation-and-MEGA_GC-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/skepta">Skepta</a>昨晚（9 月 14 日）在其品牌 MAINS 的一场时装秀上与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">Kanye West</a>首演了一首新歌。看看下面。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kanye-west-ty-dolla-sign-vultures-1-review-lyrics-tracklist-3585917">Kanye West 和 Ty Dolla $ign – “Vultures 1”评论：深陷厌女症</a></li></ul><p>这首未发行的歌曲被粉丝称为“摇钱树”，自 8 月中旬以来一直受到嘲笑，当时韦斯特在洛杉矶举行的“Vultures 2”聆听派对上首次分享了一段片段。</p><p>昨晚，Skepta 在他的品牌 MAINS 的一场时装秀上分享了这首歌的新预告片。这首歌包括歌词“<em>当战争时期，我去兰博/你想要踢踏舞，你想要桑博/楼层太多，我有足够的/我只是给予和离开，就像我计划的那样</em>。”</p><p>目前尚不清楚这首歌曲是否会收录在 Skepta 即将发行的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/skepta-announces-details-of-new-album-knife-and-fork-3564318">《Knife and Fork》</a>中，该专辑将结束歌迷自 2019 年的《Ignorance is Bliss》以来五年的等待。即将推出的第六张专辑尚未确定发行日期。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Kanye West，Skepta - 摇钱树 |新预览" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/U0wE8FIKfFc?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="da" dir="ltr">坎耶 X 斯凯普塔</p><p>“摇钱树”</p><p>另一个片段<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f6a8.png" alt="🚨" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/ZhQFNCFKM2">pic.twitter.com/ZhQFNCFKM2</a></p><p> — 英国说唱日报 (@UKRapDaily) <a href="https://twitter.com/UKRapDaily/status/1823659381197590545?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 8 月 14 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>据<em><a href="https://www.voguebusiness.com/fashion/british-rapper-skepta-revives-mains-fashion-brand" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vogue</a></em>报道，MAINS 最初由 Skepta 于 2017 年推出，两年后，由于他与当时的合作伙伴制造商“友好”分手，他将其搁置。 MAINS 随后于 2022 年复活。在昨晚的演出前不久， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/skepta-puts-out-open-casting-call-for-next-mains-fashion-runway-show-3761564">Skepta 宣布公开招募模特</a>。</p><p>这并不是两人第一次相遇。 2018 年，Skepta 与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wiley">Wiley</a>一起为 West 的专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/kanye-west-ye-review-2331315">ye</a> 》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/skepta-drake-and-wiley-are-all-credited-on-kayne-wests-ye-2339028">担任作曲家</a>。他们为唱片揭幕战“I Thought About Killing You”做出了贡献。</p><p>在此之前，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-377-1219183">据报道，两位说唱歌手曾于 2015 年在录音室一起工作</a>，当时韦斯特在全英音乐奖上表演，当时他<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/wiley-on-why-kanye-wests-brit-awards-salute-to-grime-was-empowering-not-patronising-759925">邀请了伦敦主持人和英国 grime 界的其他人来表演《All Day》</a> 。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="全天（2015 年全英音乐奖现场直播）（Explicit）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_ABk7TmjnVk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>今年早些时候，Skepta 推出了短片<em>《Tribal Mark》</em> ，这是他作为联合导演和主演的电影处女作。自该片上映以来，Skepta 告诉<em>NME</em> ，他计划 <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/skepta-tribal-mark-film-james-bond-3580027">推出一部完整的故事片来延续它的故事</a>。</p><p> “这就像每个人都试图做的黑人<em>詹姆斯·邦德</em>的事情，”斯克普塔说。 “我们想在我拍完电影后制作一些东西，我想，‘好吧，酷——现在这是特许经营权了。’” </p><figure id="attachment_3580835" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3580835" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3580835" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skepta_Portrait_Tribal_Mark.jpg" alt="斯克普塔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skepta_Portrait_Tribal_Mark.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skepta_Portrait_Tribal_Mark-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skepta_Portrait_Tribal_Mark-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skepta_Portrait_Tribal_Mark-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skepta_Portrait_Tribal_Mark-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skepta_Portrait_Tribal_Mark-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3580835" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：1PLUS1 制作</figcaption></figure><p>与此同时，West 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ty-dolla-ign">Ty Dolla $ign</a>在今年早些时候推出了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-ty-dolla-sign-release-vultures-2-deluxe-with-new-track-3781830">“Vultures 2”</a> —— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-shares-dramatic-vultures-trailer-releases-dates-three-volumes-new-music-3575720" target="_blank" rel="noopener">他们的“Vultures”合作专辑三部曲</a>的第二部分。该纪录比原计划晚了五个月。</p><p>这张专辑最初被认为会登上 Billboard 200 排行榜榜首，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>(Taylor Swift) 的最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">《The Tortured Poet&#39;s Department》</a>挡住了他的榜首位置，结束了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-wests-19-year-streak-of-number-one-album-debuts-broken-by-taylor-swift-3783078">他长达 19 年的专辑首张专辑排名第一的记录。 。</a></p><p>早在二月份，两人就推出了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kanye-west-ty-dolla-sign-vultures-1-review-lyrics-tracklist-3585917">《Vultures 1》</a> —— <em>《NME》</em>称该专辑“远非他最好的作品之一”，而且“陷入了厌女症”。它有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/freddie-gibbs">Freddie Gibbs</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yg">YG</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/playboi-carti">Playboi Carti</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">Travis Scott</a> 、West 的女儿 North 等人的特色。</p><p>自发行以来， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-and-ty-dolla-igns-vultures-2-has-now-dropped-heres-how-people-are-reacting-3780628">《Vultures 2》引起了歌迷和评论家的褒贬不一的反应</a>，并且还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/geoff-barrow-claims-kanye-west-ty-dolla-ign-didnt-have-permission-to-sample-portishead-on-vultures-2-3780721">引起了杰夫·巴罗 (Geoff Barrow) 的批评</a>，他暗示两位说唱歌手未经许可在《Vultures 2》曲目中采样了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/portishead">波蒂斯黑德 (Portishead)</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3782073" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3782073" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3782073" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images.jpg" alt="坎耶·韦斯特。图片来源：Gotham/GC Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3782073" class="wp-caption-text">坎耶·韦斯特。图片来源：Gotham/GC Images</figcaption></figure><p> The <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beak">Beak>;</a>成员在 X/Twitter 上发布了一段由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/don-toliver">Don Toliver</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kodak-black">Kodak Black</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/playboi-carti">Playboi Carti</a>主演的“Field Trip”片段，据报道还试玩了 Portishead 的“Machine Gun”。</p><p> “FFS。不会再有一次”，他写道，似乎指的是另一次未经许可就拍摄歌曲的情况。 “他为什么不能写自己的节奏？”</p><p>最初的“Vultures”专辑也遇到了类似的涉嫌侵犯版权的问题， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-and-donna-summers-estate-reach-settlement-over-use-of-i-feel-love-3768363">West 和 Donna Summer 的遗产管理机构就“Vultures 1”中涉嫌“非法”使用“I Feel Love”达成和解</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-on-confronting-kanye-west-for-sampling-his-song-without-permission-its-wrong-if-you-dont-say-anything-about-him-3593757">奥兹·奥斯本还威胁要对未经授权的黑色安息日样品采取法律行动</a>。</p><p>今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kanye-west-ride-a-horse-into-his-vultures-2-listening-experience-in-south-korea-3786287">韦斯特骑马参加了在韩国举行的“Vultures 2”聆听派对</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/skepta-shares-new-snippet-of-song-with-kanye-west-at-mains-fashion-show-3793874">Skepta 在 MAINS 时装秀上与 Kanye West 分享新歌曲片段的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
