了克劳福德</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ufc-mistake-terence-crawford-for-kendrick-lamar-at-sphere-las-vegas-3793862">UFC 赛后在拉斯维加斯 Sphere 比赛中将特伦斯·克劳福德 (Terence Crawford) 误认为肯德里克·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar) 的事件</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Terence-Crawford-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Alberto-E.-Rodriguez_Getty-Images-and-David-Crotty_Patrick-McMullan-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="特伦斯·克劳福德和肯德里克·拉马尔。图片来源：Alberto E. Rodriguez/Getty Images 和 David Crotty/Patrick McMullan via Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Terence-Crawford-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Alberto-E.-Rodriguez_Getty-Images-and-David-Crotty_Patrick-McMullan-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Terence-Crawford-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Alberto-E.-Rodriguez_Getty-Images-and-David-Crotty_Patrick-McMullan-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Terence-Crawford-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Alberto-E.-Rodriguez_Getty-Images-and-David-Crotty_Patrick-McMullan-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Terence-Crawford-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Alberto-E.-Rodriguez_Getty-Images-and-David-Crotty_Patrick-McMullan-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Terence-Crawford-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Alberto-E.-Rodriguez_Getty-Images-and-David-Crotty_Patrick-McMullan-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Terence-Crawford-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Alberto-E.-Rodriguez_Getty-Images-and-David-Crotty_Patrick-McMullan-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨晚（9 月 14 日），拳击世界冠军特伦斯·克劳福德在 UFC 306 的电视转播中被错误地标记为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Kendrick-Lamar">肯德里克·拉马尔</a>。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/drake-and-kendrick-lamars-feud-the-full-timeline-3754820">德雷克和肯德里克·拉马尔的不和：完整的时间表</a></strong></li></ul><p>克劳福德坐在拉斯维加斯 The Sphere 体育馆的笼边观看 UFC 306。此次赛事是首个在耗资 23 亿美元的竞技场举办的格斗运动赛事， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-sphere-shows-nothing-like-it-in-the-world-3435095">U2</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phish">Phish</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dead-company">Dead &amp; Company</a>都曾在此举办过驻场演出。</p><p>然而，当镜头转向克劳福德时，粉丝们注意到他被错误地标记为说唱歌手拉马尔。</p><p>观众很快在社交媒体上做出了反应，前 UFC 冠军阿尔贾曼·斯特林 (Aljamain Sterling) 是最先在 Twitter/X 上发表评论的人之一：“特伦斯·克劳福德今晚演变成肯德里克·拉马尔。”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> UFC广播让特伦斯·克劳福德对肯德里克·拉马尔感到困惑<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f62d.png" alt="??" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f62d.png" alt="??" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f62d.png" alt="??" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/UFC?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#UFC</a> <a href="https://t.co/q8mnOUAgSO">pic.twitter.com/q8mnOUAgSO</a></p><p> — 萨米·乌拉 (@Samiii90210) <a href="https://twitter.com/Samiii90210/status/1835184140821393415?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 9 月 15 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">特伦斯·克劳福德今晚演变成肯德里克·拉马尔<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f923.png" alt="🤣" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f923.png" alt="🤣" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: